description: Eamon Ryan said there had been a "lack of immediate transparency and communication" from Mr Hogan.
title: Irish government has 'lost confidence' in Hogan - Eamon Ryan
title_page: Irish government has 'lost confidence' in Hogan - Eamon Ryan - BBC News
maintext: "My message is the virus hasn't gone away. We are at a tipping point in Ireland right now. We must do everything we can to avoid another national lockdown."
